title: Watch 'Empire' Stars Have Fun Messing With Taraji P. Henson On Set
text:
Watch 'Empire' Stars Have Fun Messing With Taraji P. Henson On Set We can't wait for Taraji's revenge. Cole Delbyck Entertainment Writer, The Huffington Post Posted: 10/22/2015 05:07 PM EDT Kevin Winter via Getty Images 
Stars take embarrassing videos of friends without their consent -- they're just like us! 
The latest victim of video prankery is "Empire" matriarch Taraji P. Henson. In the video compilation below (via Facebook), "Empire" stars Jussie Smollett and Bryshere Y. Gray capture Henson on set sleeping, singing and rapping much to the chagrin of the "Hustle & Flow" actress.
